input.content:
# Claude Code 配置完全指南

## 配置文件位置

- Windows: `C:\Users\<用户名>\.claude\settings.json`
- macOS/Linux: `~/.claude/settings.json`

## 1. API Key 和端点配置

### 方法一：直接配置环境变量

```json
{
  "env": {
    "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "sk-ant-api03-xxxxx",
    "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "https://api.anthropic.com"
  }
}
```

### 方法二：使用代理（你当前的方式）

```json
{
  "env": {
    "ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN": "PROXY_MANAGED",
    "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "http://127.0.0.1:15721"
  }
}
```

### 方法三：使用 API Key Helper 脚本

```json
{
  "apiKeyHelper": "/path/to/get-api-key.sh"
}
```

脚本示例 `get-api-key.sh`:
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# 从密钥管理器获取 API Key
echo "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=$(security find-generic-password -s anthropic -w)"
```

### 方法四：AWS Bedrock 配置

```json
{
  "env": {
    "AWS_REGION": "us-east-1",
    "AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID": "your-access-key",
    "AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY": "your-secret-key"
  },
  "awsCredentialExport": "/path/to/aws-credentials.sh",
  "awsAuthRefresh": "/path/to/aws-refresh.sh"
}
```

## 2. 自定义 API 端点

### OpenRouter

```json
{
  "env": {
    "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "sk-or-v1-xxxxx",
    "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "https://openrouter.ai/api/v1"
  }
}
```

### Azure OpenAI

```json
{
  "env": {
    "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "your-azure-key",
    "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "https://your-resource.openai.azure.com"
  }
}
```

### 自建代理

```json
{
  "env": {
    "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "your-key",
    "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "https://your-proxy.com/v1",
    "HTTP_PROXY": "http://proxy.company.com:8080",
    "HTTPS_PROXY": "http://proxy.company.com:8080",
    "NO_PROXY": "localhost,127.0.0.1"
  }
}
```

## 3. 模型配置

### 指定默认模型

```json
{
  "model": "claude-opus-4-6"
}
```

可选值：
- `claude-opus-4-6` - 最强大
- `claude-sonnet-4-6` - 平衡（默认）
- `claude-haiku-4-5` - 最快最便宜

### 限制可用模型（企业管理）

```json
{
  "availableModels": ["opus-4-6", "sonnet-4-6"]
}
```

## 4. 权限配置

### 完整权限配置示例

```json
{
  "permissions": {
    "defaultMode": "bypassPermissions",
    "allow": [
      "Read(*)",
      "Write(*)",
      "Edit(*)",
      "Bash(*)",
      "Grep(*)",
      "Glob(*)"
    ],
    "deny": [
      "Bash(rm -rf /)",
      "Write(/etc/**)",
      "Edit(/etc/**)"
    ],
    "ask": [
      "Bash(git push*)",
      "Bash(npm publish*)"
    ],
    "additionalDirectories": [
      "/home/user/projects",
      "/mnt/data"
    ]
  }
}
```

### 权限模式说明

- `acceptEdits` - 自动接受编辑操作
- `bypassPermissions` - 绕过所有权限提示
- `default` - 默认模式（会提示）
- `dontAsk` - 不询问
- `plan` - 计划模式

### 权限规则语法

- `*` - 匹配所有
- `Read(*.py)` - 只允许读取 Python 文件
- `Bash(git *)` - 只允许 git 命令
- `Write(/home/user/*)` - 只允许写入特定目录

## 5. MCP 服务器配置

### 基础 MCP 配置

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "memory": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@modelcontextprotocol/server-memory"]
    },
    "filesystem": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem", "/allowed/path"]
    },
    "github": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@modelcontextprotocol/server-github"],
      "env": {
        "GITHUB_TOKEN": "ghp_xxxxx"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### 自定义 MCP 服务器

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "custom-server": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["/path/to/server.py"],
      "env": {
        "API_KEY": "your-key",
        "DEBUG": "true"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### MCP 服务器白名单/黑名单（企业管理）

```json
{
  "allowedMcpServers": [
    {
      "serverName": "memory",
      "serverCommand": ["npx", "-y", "@modelcontextprotocol/server-memory"]
    }
  ],
  "deniedMcpServers": [
    {
      "serverName": "dangerous-server"
    }
  ]
}
```

## 6. 钩子配置

### 命令钩子

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [{
      "matcher": "*",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "echo 'Claude Code 启动'",
        "statusMessage": "初始化环境..."
      }]
    }],
    "PreToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Write",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "git add .",
        "async": true
      }]
    }],
    "PostToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Edit",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "prettier --write {{file_path}}",
        "timeout": 5000
      }]
    }]
  }
}
```

### LLM 提示钩子

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "PreToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Bash",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "prompt",
        "prompt": "检查这个命令是否安全：$ARGUMENTS",
        "model": "claude-haiku-4-5"
      }]
    }]
  }
}
```

### Agent 验证钩子

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Bash(npm test*)",
